1
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,350
Move, move, move!

2
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:48,000
This is a world of wolves and tigers.

3
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:51,200
Drifting like duckweed, lives like grass.

4
00:01:51,430 --> 00:01:52,480
In order to survive...

5
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,920
You must use every ounce of your strength.

6
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:58,230
Winners become kings, losers become bandits.

7
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:00,870
Use your strength to prove...

8
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,480
Which one of you is the king.

9
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:04,510
A bunch of rabble.

10
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,430
Doing nothing but wicked deeds.

11
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,000
We have no quarrel with you.

12
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:10,150
Why make us kill each other?

13
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:12,640
Because of this.

14
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:14,640
I won't lay a hand on those two.

15
00:02:14,950 --> 00:02:15,630
If you want a fight...

16
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,430
Have your men fight me instead.

17
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,560
You got a death wish?

18
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:20,430
Boss Ma, let me handle this.

19
00:02:21,910 --> 00:02:23,520
Why do you always have to jump in?

20
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,560
Defeat your opponent, and you live.

21
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:42,590
Fight! Fight! Fight!

22
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:48,680
Brother, forgive me.

23
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:50,870
Place your bets! Place your bets!

24
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:52,960
Big bowl for the tall one, small bowl for the short one.

25
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,960
You bet on the short one, I'll bet on the tall one.

26
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,430
Big Brother, they're gambling with lives.

27
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,840
Good!

28
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:53,280
Get him! Get him!

29
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:18,960
Yeah!

30
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:21,520
Get up! Get up!

31
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,800
Get up! Get up!

32
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,120
The tall one won!

33
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:32,830
The tall one won!

34
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,430
The tall one won!

35
00:04:40,190 --> 00:04:41,190
Wait a minute, wait, wait!

36
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:42,190
Boss Ma.

37
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,430
Didn't we just agree...

38
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:45,160
That the winner gets to live?

39
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,040
Why are you feeding him poison?

40
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,680
Today is a good day.

41
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,680
We return with a full load.

42
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:54,950
Can you do me a favor?

43
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:57,190
Let that bastard who won go.

44
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:58,870
You think he's pitiful?

45
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,240
Then you take it.

46
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:02,750
What?

47
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,750
Why feed it to me?

48
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,800
What is this stuff? Is it poison?

49
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,560
What's going on?

50
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:26,600
Swap him with the winner.

51
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:29,630
I can't take it anymore.

52
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,070
You can.

53
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:35,040
You are my handpicked Strategist.

54
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,920
I once had a beloved.

55
00:06:31,630 --> 00:06:35,270
We were childhood sweethearts, deeply in love.

56
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:37,830
We pledged our lives to each other.

57
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,750
Suddenly...

58
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:44,480
A demon in a military uniform barged in.

59
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:49,190
To reach an agreement with the bandits...

60
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,720
The demon sent me up the mountain.

61
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,950
To become the real bandit chief...

62
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,120
Tiger Ma's Captive Wife.

63
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,950
Who would have thought that demon...

64
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,310
Would break his word.

65
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:04,720
He ambushed us when our guard was down.

66
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,510
And killed the real Tiger Ma.

67
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,430
Before he died...

68
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:11,600
He entrusted all this to me.

69
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,920
I want revenge.

70
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,040
I want revenge.

71
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:19,120
I must have revenge.

72
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:25,360
I am a weak woman, all alone.

73
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,680
Are you willing to help me?

74
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,360
When it is done...

75
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,390
I will give myself to you.

76
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,390
Are you willing to become my Deathsworn?

77
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,950
To die for me?

78
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,680
Who are you?

79
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:46,680
Why should I die for you?

80
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:49,070
I am the one you worry about...

81
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:51,680
The one haunting your dreams.

82
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,680
Yu Zhen.

83
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,120
Who is Yu Zhen?

84
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,630
My Missus.

85
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:03,240
You're willing to die for your Missus?

86
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,920
You love your Missus that much?

87
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:10,800
I love only her.

88
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,240
I think you want to die.

89
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:18,680
You and your...

90
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,160
Childhood sweethearts.

91
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:25,000
You and your Tiger Ma.

92
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:28,750
Are just like me and my Yu Zhen.

93
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:55,120
Did I fall asleep?

94
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:56,600
You were talking in your sleep.

95
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,790
I dreamt you didn't want to be Tiger Ma.

96
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:02,390
But you had no choice but to be Tiger Ma.

97
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:05,150
You poor thing.

98
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,790
I *am* Tiger Ma.

99
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,870
I was born to be Tiger Ma.

100
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,630
No.

101
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:15,080
I've always felt you're a good person.

102
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:18,150
You look better with two braids.

103
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:33,720
The same kind of night.

104
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,550
The same place.

105
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,840
The same rain falling.

106
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:42,240
The things you did to me.

107
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:44,240
The words you said.

108
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,390
They're all right here.

109
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:52,630
I'll never forget them as long as I live.

110
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:55,840
I am your true Deathsworn.

111
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:59,270
Having just me as your Deathsworn is enough.

112
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:06,360
It's enough.

113
00:10:08,390 --> 00:10:09,550
Big Brother.

114
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,120
You need to broaden your horizons.

115
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:16,120
My sister isn't the only woman here.

116
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:18,790
You should take a look around...

117
00:10:20,030 --> 00:10:23,000
...at the other women in the stronghold.

118
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,720
You don't understand.

119
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:33,750
I do understand.

120
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:40,030
Go away.

121
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,750
Hurry up and go.

122
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,720
Come back here.

123
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:57,600
Big Brother.

124
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,720
Stop drinking.

125
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:08,120
But in my heart...

126
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:10,030
...there is only Tiger Ma.

127
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,550
I'm sorry.

128
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,150
Zhen'er.

129
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:37,120
Mom wants to talk something over with you.

130
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:39,480
I'll find you a new husband.

131
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,720
Are you willing?

132
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:41,840
Mom.

133
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:44,510
Don't bring that up.

134
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:47,510
Let me tell you, what you did that day...

135
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:49,080
...you did one thing right.

136
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,840
And you did one thing wrong.

137
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,510
The right thing was...

138
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:54,150
...not leaving with Fan Bao.

139
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:56,080
The wrong thing is...

140
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,150
...you're still thinking about that Sha'er.

141
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,120
He's dead and gone.

142
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:08,750
Let me tell you the truth.

143
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,390
Sha'er didn't die.

144
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:14,150
No... no...

145
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,910
Even if he's not dead, you must treat him as dead.

146
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:21,270
That day when Fan Bao and Master Wen went back...

147
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:24,550
...the elders all found out Fan Sha'er isn't dead.

148
00:12:24,550 --> 00:12:25,320
Do you understand?

149
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,390
He's colluding with bandits.

150
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:30,360
Do you know what a huge crime collusion with bandits is?

151
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,670
Do you think those elders will let him off?

152
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:34,390
I know him.

153
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,360
No matter how immature he is...

154
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,630
...he wouldn't collude with bandits.

155
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,670
He did it to protect his brothers.

156
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:43,550
His own great-uncle wanted to bury him alive.

157
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:45,360
Why are you so silly?

158
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,550
He is my man, after all.

159
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,200
Now that I know where he is...

160
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,960
...I definitely have to go find him.

161
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,720
Stop pretending.

162
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,550
You're used to pretending.

163
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,030
I'm not pretending.

164
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,550
Go find him then.

165
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,630
Can you actually find him?

166
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:22,360
Is he really like Fan Bao said?

167
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,840
Opened a hotpot place? Making money?

168
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,360
What if Fan Bao is lying to you?

169
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,440
Just to comfort you?

170
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:32,320
That Sha'er left the Fan family.

171
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,960
He is nothing.

172
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:35,910
So what if you find him?

173
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,030
He has no money.

174
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,840
How will you live?

175
00:13:38,910 --> 00:13:39,720
Mom.

176
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,840
Don't worry about that.

177
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:47,840
This time,

178
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,630
whether it's true or false,

179
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,030
dead or alive,

180
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:53,320
I have to see for myself.

181
00:13:54,790 --> 00:13:56,000
I've made up my mind.

182
00:13:57,030 --> 00:13:58,000
Don't try to stop me.

183
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:58,790
You dare!

184
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,750
Get back here!

185
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:06,550
Take care of yourself.

186
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:09,510
Don't worry about me.

187
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:18,840
Get back here!

188
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,200
You... You...

189
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,080
Are you coming back?

190
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,600
If you don't come back,

191
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,670
I'll act like I never had you!

192
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:28,000
Don't ever come back!

193
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:30,550
You godforsaken, ungrateful brat!

194
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:43,790
Division Commander Chen said,

195
00:14:44,030 --> 00:14:45,480
he's seeing no one today.

196
00:14:45,870 --> 00:14:46,480
Brother.

197
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,670
We're from the Huo family.

198
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,120
Division Commander Chen rules this area.

199
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,960
Our business,

200
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:55,360
he should preside over it.

201
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,440
Quit making a scene!

202
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,240
I don't care who you are.

203
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,440
Get out!

204
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,440
What's going on here?

205
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:06,080
It's a racket.

206
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:07,320
Fifth Concubine.

207
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:09,120
You have to help me this time.

208
00:15:19,510 --> 00:15:22,360
I just want to stay under Division Commander Chen's rule

209
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,630
and do a little business in peace.

210
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:26,790
Who knew bandits were so rampant?

211
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,390
They have no respect for you, Commander.

212
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:32,360
That your goods were robbed is a minor issue.

213
00:15:32,550 --> 00:15:33,960
But they are so arrogant.

214
00:15:34,150 --> 00:15:36,600
It's a slap in Old Chen's face.

215
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:37,670
Exactly.

216
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:39,360
They even dared to rob my goods.

217
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:40,960
What about the people under your rule?

218
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,960
Aren't they living in fear every day?

219
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:45,440
So, regarding bandit suppression,

220
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:47,150
it's not just for me.

221
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:50,000
It's for the people under Division Commander Chen.

222
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:52,360
We must wipe out these bandits.

223
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:56,360
Our Old Chen cares about the people.

224
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:58,240
I don't need you to remind me.

225
00:15:58,360 --> 00:15:59,440
Yes, yes, yes.

226
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,960
The leader is that guy named Fan.

227
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,270
Named Fan?

228
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:07,960
That's right.

229
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:10,200
The one who opened the hotpot place in town.

230
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:13,000
Commander Qin even wanted to support him.

231
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,670
Who knew he'd be so ungrateful?

232
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,120
Under Division Commander Chen's rule,

233
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,870
he made a fortune.

234
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,870
Then he turned around and colluded with bandits.

235
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:22,200
How can someone be so unethical?

236
00:16:22,510 --> 00:16:23,790
If we let this slide,

237
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:25,910
what will happen in the future?

238
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:26,870
Alright, alright.

239
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:28,240
I know.

240
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:29,960
Old Chen,

241
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:33,000
you can't ignore this.

242
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:40,870
As the old saying goes:

243
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:44,670
"Good harvest, full bellies."

244
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:48,550
"Pest plague, starving ghosts."

245
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,910
Once there's a plague of pests,

246
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,960
the price of pesticide goes up.

247
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,390
You're a businessman.

248
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:56,200
Do you think the common folk

249
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,030
should stock up on pesticide,

250
00:16:58,440 --> 00:17:01,600
or should I ban merchants from raising prices?

251
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:05,840
Division Commander Chen,

252
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:09,630
where there's demand, there's supply.

253
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:27,310
If Division Commander Chen has any concerns,

254
00:17:27,310 --> 00:17:28,240
just say the word.

255
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:30,960
To be able to solve problems for Division Commander Chen

256
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:33,400
is an honor for the Huo family.

257
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:38,070
Young Master Huo is a sincere man.

258
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:39,750
Then from now on, in our dealings,

259
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:41,830
let's lay our cards on the table.

260
00:17:42,510 --> 00:17:43,310
Openly.

261
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:45,480
In the future,

262
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,550
don't go behind my back.

263
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:54,110
Understood, understood, understood.

264
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,160
I'm planning to run away.

265
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:13,310
You run, hurry.

266
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:14,680
Run as far away as possible.

267
00:18:15,590 --> 00:18:18,480
I mean us taking the crew and running together.

268
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:20,160
Why together?

269
00:18:20,270 --> 00:18:21,270
Keep it down.

270
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,240
Brother Fan.

271
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,160
Last night,

272
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,030
what was the situation?

273
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:29,070
Why do you care what the situation was?

274
00:18:30,550 --> 00:18:31,920
If we keep staying here,

275
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,680
if we're not killed by Tiger Ma,

276
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,310
we'll die for her sake.

277
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,880
What? What? What are you guys talking about?

278
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,960
If we don't run,

279
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:42,590
it's definitely a dead end.

280
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:44,310
She has her difficulties.

281
00:18:44,510 --> 00:18:46,310
That doesn't mean she can kill people indiscriminately.

282
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:48,920
No sense of honor.

283
00:18:49,030 --> 00:18:50,030
Exactly, exactly.

284
00:18:50,030 --> 00:18:50,920
Honor?

285
00:18:51,030 --> 00:18:52,480
What kind of honor is that?

286
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:53,640
Before getting married,

287
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:55,720
wandering the world, brothers came first.

288
00:18:56,590 --> 00:19:00,030
Got a woman, and you forgot what brothers are.

289
00:19:01,270 --> 00:19:02,550
That's love, you know.

290
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:03,960
His love has to be understood,

291
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:05,440
but others' love gets ignored?

292
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:10,110
Did I hit a nerve?

293
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:11,510
Biting the hand that feeds you.

294
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:13,960
You got special treatment as soon as you arrived.

295
00:19:14,350 --> 00:19:15,510
Ask the brothers,

296
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,000
who else enjoyed that?

297
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:20,510
You're so favored, yet not satisfied.

298
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:22,640
And you want to undermine her?

299
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:27,830
I don't want this kind of favor.

300
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:29,070
You go, you go.

301
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:30,200
What you don't want

302
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:31,830
is what others dream of.

303
00:19:35,030 --> 00:19:36,070
I get it.

304
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:38,640
Big Brother has fallen for Tiger Ma.

305
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,590
You shut up.

306
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:42,790
If you want to leave, go by yourself.

307
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:43,960
I won't leave.

308
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,440
Me not snitching

309
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:47,550
is already for the sake of our past brotherhood.

310
00:20:06,510 --> 00:20:07,750
A caravan is passing at the foot of the mountain.

311
00:20:07,750 --> 00:20:08,750
Get ready to move out.

312
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:10,480
Didn't we just pull a job?

313
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,790
Why go again?

314
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,160
That haul could last us a long time.

315
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:15,480
Sometimes it's not just about being full.

316
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:17,550
Strategist, if you don't want to go,

317
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:18,880
you can stay home and watch the house.

318
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,000
How can I do that?

319
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:20,960
Everyone goes.

320
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,110
Big Brother.

321
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,200
Think about it.

322
00:20:25,270 --> 00:20:26,590
Don't talk to me.

323
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:27,590
I don't want to listen.

324
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,960
Then everyone goes.

325
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:38,880
I came too, didn't I?

326
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:41,110
Against those scumbags,

327
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:43,400
I don't even need a weapon.

328
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,590
They're here.

329
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:05,440
In position.

330
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:19,400
Don't chop, don't chop, don't chop!

331
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:21,110
Chop fast, chop fast!

332
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,640
He said chop faster!

333
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,480
Go!

334
00:22:12,310 --> 00:22:14,200
Charge! Hurry!

335
00:22:20,350 --> 00:22:21,310
Run!

336
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:22,880
Run, run fast!

337
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:43,000
Scarface, take care of her.

338
00:22:43,350 --> 00:22:44,110
Go, come on.

339
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:48,240
Hurry up.

340
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:53,240
Quick, retreat, retreat!

341
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:01,680
Sister Hua!

342
00:23:02,030 --> 00:23:02,640
Sister Hua!

343
00:23:16,750 --> 00:23:17,510
Stop.

344
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:24,920
Where is Sister Hua?

345
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,510
She was with Scarface, right?

346
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:29,350
Here they come.

347
00:23:34,550 --> 00:23:35,510
Where is Sister Hua?

348
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:38,030
She's dead.

349
00:23:39,110 --> 00:23:40,070
There's a blood trail.

350
00:23:40,350 --> 00:23:41,680
Follow the blood trail, chase!

351
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:49,590
You'll only drag everyone down like this.

352
00:23:53,350 --> 00:23:54,590
Go, hurry up.

353
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:08,110
Where are the bloodstains?

354
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:09,070
They're gone.

355
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:11,070
You keep chasing. I'll go report.

356
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:26,830
Report!

357
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:27,510
Reporting, Commander.

358
00:24:27,510 --> 00:24:28,750
We found a trail of blood.

359
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:29,480
Where?

360
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:30,640
It...

361
00:24:30,790 --> 00:24:32,720
It disappeared.

362
00:24:33,070 --> 00:24:33,750
Commander.

363
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:36,240
I'll take some men to pursue.

364
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:37,070
Hold on.

365
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:39,030
Division Commander Chen gave orders.

366
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,790
We must preserve our strength.

367
00:24:41,480 --> 00:24:42,790
We have to catch that guy Fan.

368
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:44,030
And get your revenge.

369
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:45,310
I do want revenge.

370
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:47,790
But chasing further might lead into an ambush.

371
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,400
Since we can already claim victory...

372
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:51,750
...we should quit while we're ahead.

373
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,270
Just giving the Huos an explanation will do.

374
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:55,270
Withdraw.

375
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,310
Commander!

376
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,110
Withdraw!

377
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:58,440
Yes, sir.

378
00:24:58,550 --> 00:25:00,000
Commander Qin is a piece of trash.

379
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:01,240
A rotten scumbag.

380
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:02,830
Playing dumb to take it all.

381
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:04,960
We spent so much money.

382
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:07,240
Surely it hasn't gone down the drain?

383
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:07,880
No way.

384
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,070
I'm going to find Division Commander Chen.

385
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:10,590
Stop.

386
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:13,480
Who are you to go find him?

387
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:15,480
If he really wanted to suppress bandits...

388
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:18,070
...it wouldn't end up like this.

389
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,070
These ungrateful people, these insatiable dogs.

390
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:25,240
A bunch of profit-seeking, greedy jerks.

391
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,590
Young Master, all these years...

392
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:28,270
...you haven't skimped on greasing their palms.

393
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:30,680
Even a weight dropped in water makes a bubble.

394
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:32,880
They can't even handle these small matters.

395
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,480
Scum.

396
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:36,270
Alright, alright, alright.

397
00:25:36,720 --> 00:25:37,640
Calm down.

398
00:25:38,310 --> 00:25:40,240
If these words get out...

399
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,110
...even I won't be able to save you.

400
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:47,880
So what can we do now?

401
00:25:48,270 --> 00:25:49,480
We can't just let it go.

402
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:50,440
Let it go?

403
00:25:51,110 --> 00:25:52,310
Things have reached this point.

404
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:53,830
Even God himself couldn't make me let it go.

405
00:26:03,350 --> 00:26:05,720
Don't we still have Xiu Gu in our hands...

406
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:06,920
...and her old man?

407
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:10,200
We just need to keep Fan Sha'er in check.

408
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:12,160
Fan Sha'er won't just ignore...

409
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,790
...Xiu Gu and her father.

410
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:27,510
Come here.

411
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:29,200
Take off your pants.

412
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:33,480
Huh? What? Are you shy?

413
00:26:33,750 --> 00:26:34,590
Take them off yourself.

414
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:58,960
Is this thing poisonous?

415
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:01,640
Us wandering practitioners...

416
00:27:02,070 --> 00:27:03,640
...know a little bit of everything.

417
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,550
It'll get better slowly. Come on.

418
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:20,750
It does feel better.

419
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:26,030
How did you know there was a cave here?

420
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:29,110
Tiger Ma brought me here before.

421
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:32,240
I know.

422
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:34,960
You don't truly want to be a bandit.

423
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,510
I don't want blood on my hands.

424
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:43,240
Killing people indiscriminately.

425
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,880
In this world...

426
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:50,350
it's unavoidable.

427
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:56,640
Nice guys finish last.

428
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:59,070
You don't want to kill indiscriminately.

429
00:27:59,830 --> 00:28:01,270
But the one who ends up dead...

430
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,750
...will be you.

431
00:28:03,830 --> 00:28:07,240
Humans are born good by nature.

432
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:10,070
That's what the sages say.

433
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,920
Why don't we just not go back?

434
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:16,920
Just walk away.

435
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,440
After how Tiger Ma treated me...

436
00:28:20,110 --> 00:28:21,070
Her sister's life is a life...

437
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:22,350
but isn't my life a life too?

438
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:24,590
I've finally figured it out.

439
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:26,920
Good.

440
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,270
But I have to go back.

441
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:31,750
To take the crew with me.

442
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:35,640
Will your Big Brother listen to you?

443
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:39,070
He's just not thinking straight right now.

444
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,680
I'll make him see reason.

445
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:42,920
When it comes to love...

446
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:44,550
...can he be woken up?

447
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:49,110
Even if he hates me...

448
00:28:50,070 --> 00:28:51,440
I can't just stand by...

449
00:28:52,110 --> 00:28:54,640
...and watch him die at Tiger Ma's place.

450
00:28:59,590 --> 00:29:00,590
Counting today...

451
00:29:01,590 --> 00:29:02,790
...you've saved me twice.

452
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,270
My life...

453
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,240
...is yours.

454
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:08,680
You're too serious, too serious.

455
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:13,880
I wish to become sworn brothers with Brother Fan.

456
00:29:14,590 --> 00:29:15,720
And honor you as my Big Brother.

457
00:29:15,830 --> 00:29:17,030
I'd risk my life for you.

458
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:19,440
You can't refuse.

459
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:23,440
You've seen my ass, after all.

460
00:29:27,790 --> 00:29:28,640
Brother.

461
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,160
Big Brother.

462
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:02,830
Excuse me.

463
00:30:03,270 --> 00:30:05,550
Is the boss here named Fan?

464
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:07,960
Who are you?

465
00:30:08,350 --> 00:30:08,720
I am...

466
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:15,400
I am the owner of this shop.

467
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,160
There's no one named Fan here.

468
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:19,790
This shop...

469
00:30:20,110 --> 00:30:21,070
...belongs to the Dong family.

470
00:30:26,270 --> 00:30:27,640
I'm warning you.

471
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:30,240
Don't get involved with anyone named Fan again.
